quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,1,Haa-meem
  40,2,Iss kitab ka nazil farmana uss Allah ki taraf say hai jo ghalib aur dana hai
  40,3,Gunah ka bakhsney wala aur toba ka qabool farmaney wala sakht azab wala inam-o-qudrat wala jiss kay siwa koi mabood nahi. Ussi ki taraf wapis lotna hai
  40,4,Allah Taalaa ki aayaton mein wohi log jhagartay hain jo kafir hain pus inn logon ka shehron mein chalna phirna aap ko dhokay mein na daal day
  40,5,Qom-e-nooh ney aur unn kay baad kay girohon ney bhi jhutlaya tha. Aur her ummat ney apnay rasool ko giriftar kerleney ka iradah kiya aur baatil kay zariyey kaj behasiyan kien takay unn say haq ko bigar den pus mein ney unn ko pakar liya so meri taraf say kaisi saza hui
  40,6,Aur issi tarah aap kay rab ka hukum kafiron per sabit hogaya kay woh dozakhi hain
  40,7,Arash kay uthaney walay aur uss kay aas pass kay (farishtay) apnay rab ki tasbeeh hamd kay sath sath kertay hain aur uss per eman rakhtay hain aur eman walon kay liye istaghfaar kertay hain kehtay hain kay aey humaray perwerdigar! Tu ney her cheez ko apni bakhsish aur ilm say gher rakha hai pus tu enhen bakhash day jo toba keren aur teri raah ki perwi keren aur tu enhen dozakh kay azab say bhi bacha lay
  40,8,Aey humaray rab! Tu enhen hameshgi wali jannaton mein ley ja jin kay tu ney inn say wada kiya hai aur inn kay baap dadon aur biwiyon aur aulad mein say (bhi) inn (sab) ko jo nek amal hain. Yaqeenan tu to ghalib-o-ba-hikmat hai
  40,9,Enhen burayion say bhi mehfooz rakh hq to yeh hai kay uss din tu ney jissay burayion say bacha liya uss per tu ney rehmat kerdi aur boht bari kaamyabi to yehi hai